    <entry>
      <title>Failed to connect to github.com port 443: Timed out</title>
      <link href="/2021/08/16/port%20443/"/>
      <url>/2021/08/16/port%20443/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="起因"><a href="#起因" class="headerlink" title="起因"></a>起因</h2><p>某天hexo d上传更新至github时报此错<br>以前靠着梯子的全局代理还能抢救一下,但是今天想彻底改善一下,于是查找了解决方法.</p><h2 id="解决过程"><a href="#解决过程" class="headerlink" title="解决过程"></a>解决过程</h2><ol><li>打开git bash,运行以下代码,清除代理配置<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git config --global --unset http.proxy</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>打开ipaddress.com,查询如下两个域名，并分别记录下其对应的ip：</li></ol><ul><li>github.com</li><li>github.global.ssl.fastly.net</li></ul><ol start="3"><li>进入C:\Windows\System32\drivers\etc对hosts文件修改</li></ol><ul><li>在末尾加上以下两条(ip值根据网站查询到的进行更改)<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">192.30.253.112 github.com</span><br><span class="line">151.101.185.194 github.global.ssl.fastly.net</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><ol start="4"><li>打开cmd,清理一下DNS<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ipconfig /flushdns</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>重新打开git bash,hexo d后光速上传,问题解决.</li></ol>]]></content>
      
      
      <categories>
          
          <category> Web </category>
          
      </categories>
      
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
